{"word":"H5651 - עֶבֶד - ʻEbed - eh'-bed - Ebed","slug":"H5651","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֶבֶד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻEbed"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>eh'-bed"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ebed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עבד</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛ebed</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>eh'-bed</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Ebed = \"servant\" <ol><li>father of Gaal in the time of the judges</li><li>son of Jonathan and one of the sons of Adin who returned from exile with Ezra</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H5650\">H5650</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4566\">H4566</a>, <a href=\"#/H5647\">H5647</a>, <a href=\"#/H5650\">H5650</a>, <a href=\"#/H5652\">H5652</a>, <a href=\"#/H5653\">H5653</a>, <a href=\"#/H5654\">H5654</a>, <a href=\"#/H5655\">H5655</a>, <a href=\"#/H5656\">H5656</a>, <a href=\"#/H5657\">H5657</a>, <a href=\"#/H5658\">H5658</a>, <a href=\"#/H5659\">H5659</a>, <a href=\"#/H5660\">H5660</a>, <a href=\"#/H5661\">H5661</a>, <a href=\"#/H5662\">H5662</a>, <a href=\"#/H5663\">H5663</a>, <a href=\"#/H5664\">H5664</a>, <a href=\"#/H5744\">H5744</a>"}]}